The paper discusses approaches to improve Question Answering models, which is a common topic in the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of latent-variable methods and optimization techniques also suggests a focus on Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories.
